Receipt Delivery Type Description: "Where the carrier takes possession of a fully stuffed container delivered by the customer at the carrier or carrier's appointed supplier's facility or where a container is released to the customer by the carrier."
"Indicating that the carrier is taking possession of or delivers a fully stuffed container at the customer's appointed premises."
